Location
Contact Information
Use the information below to contact us or you may e-mail us using our
Contact Form
E-Mail:
manager@mountdorayachtclub.com
Telephone:
(352) 383-3188
Address:
351 W. Fourth Ave.
Mount Dora, Florida 32757
Directions
From U.S. Highway 441
Take State Road 46 West toward Mount Dora.
Turn right onto Highland Ave/Old Hwy 441
Turn left onto Fifth Ave.
Turn left onto McDonald St.
Right onto Fourth Ave. The street will end at the Yacht Club's parking lot.
From Old US Highway 441
Follow Old 441 into downtown Mount Dora.
Turn right onto McDonald St. (First right after Heron Cay B&B - victorian style)
Turn right onto Fourth Avenue; street will end at the Yacht Club's parking lot
